        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Airline Pilot Pension Fairness Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits a reduction in the value of pension benefits guaranteed by the Pension Benefit Guaranty Corporation for commercial airline pilots if they are required to retire before age 65 under federal aviation rules.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
